## üöÄ Key Features

### 1. "Steam Logic" Fall Detection
We solved the problem of monitoring wet bathrooms without cameras. By correlating the **Proximity Sensor** (Entry) with **Humidity Spikes** (Shower ON), the system knows when a fall is most likely to happen and tightens its safety thresholds accordingly.

### 2. Spam-Filtered Alerts
The Central Controller includes a "Cool-Down" logic to prevent alert fatigue. If a fall is detected, it suppresses duplicate emails for 60 seconds while continuing to log the event.

### 3. Automated Data Dashboard
Sensor logs are automatically written to a master Excel file (`SeniorConnect_MasterLog.xlsx`). A custom Python script pushes this file to a private GitHub repository every minute, ensuring the Workflow Team always has access to the latest health data without manual file transfers.

